  "detailed_description": "Battle Arena: Euro Wars is a turn-based action/strategy game that presents a small episode of the conflict between forces of Unity and Commune on the streets of 3 european locations.<br> <br><br><strong>Game features:</strong><br><br>- 3 maps: Germany, Sweden, Spain.<br>- 4 mission type: capture the flag, target hunting, get points, kill them all.<br>- Turn based gameplay in the form of a street fight.<br>- Single player, offline.<br>- Player vs 7 bots.<br>- At least 6 hours of gameplay to finish all missions. <br>- Two teams.<br>- 14 characters.<br>- Over 30 achievements.",
  "about_the_game": "Battle Arena: Euro Wars is a turn-based action/strategy game that presents a small episode of the conflict between forces of Unity and Commune on the streets of 3 european locations.<br> <br><br><strong>Game features:</strong><br><br>- 3 maps: Germany, Sweden, Spain.<br>- 4 mission type: capture the flag, target hunting, get points, kill them all.<br>- Turn based gameplay in the form of a street fight.<br>- Single player, offline.<br>- Player vs 7 bots.<br>- At least 6 hours of gameplay to finish all missions. <br>- Two teams.<br>- 14 characters.<br>- Over 30 achievements.",
